    {"dimension":"Conversation intelligence depth","values":{"fathom":"Recording, transcript, AI summary, action items — light by design","grain":"AI notes, smart tags, deal scorecards, coaching playlists — Gong-lite","gong":"Deep: deal scoring, forecasting, market intelligence, AI agents, win/loss"}},
