    {"question":"Fathom vs Grain vs Gong — which is best in 2026?","answer":"There is no single best — the right pick is almost entirely a function of org size. Solo founders and SMB reps should run Fathom (the free tier is unlimited recording with AI summaries). Sales teams of 5-100 reps should run Grain Business at $15/seat/mo (Gong-lite at one-eighth the cost). Orgs with 200+ reps and a RevOps function should run Gong for its forecast engine, market intelligence and AI agents. Listicles compare them as if they are the same product; they are not."},
